query: SELECT m.id, m.title, m.authors, e.id as eval_id, e.overall_score, e.verdict, e.created_at FROM manuals m LEFT JOIN evaluations e ON m.id = e.manual_id WHERE m.title LIKE '%Principi di Chimica%' AND m.authors LIKE '%Atkins%' ORDER BY m.created_at DESC LIMIT 1;
